<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Niklas von Kospoth, Vogt zu Hohenberg an der Eger</head><p>Der Rat versichert die Freundschaft wegen Jobist N., der zuvor Niklas Erhart gedient hat.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_48" id="23r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_48_r1l15">Nykeln von Koſpad
<del rend="strikethrough">d</del> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l16">voyt cʒu hohemberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_48_r1l17">Lyber her voyt . Als Jr vns <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l18"><expan>ein<ex>n</ex>s</expan> <expan>knab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wegen genant Jobiſt / der von Nykel Erharten cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l19">euch kumen ſeẏ / der doch wider vns nÿe getan hab . als das wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l20">wiſſentlich 
<add><ab facs="#facs_48_line_1577010057671_1770">ſey etc </ab></add> . Alſo wöllen wir <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> ſchreẏben darümb wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l21"><expan>gelawb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . vnd euch des günnen / vnd Jm fürbaʒ durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vville<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l22">keins argen darümb gewarten / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo vvir euch lieb oder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l23">freuntſchaft bevveiſen möhten . das teten vvir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ııj̃ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l24"><expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Barth<ex>olomei</ex></expan> <expan>ap<ex>oſto</ex>lı</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_48" id="23r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Nykeln von Kospad, voyt czu Hohemberg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lyber her voyt, als ir uns <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von <expan>ein<ex>n</ex>s</expan>
<expan>knab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wegen genant Jobist, der von Nykel Erharten
                        czu euch kumen sey, der doch wider uns nye getan hab, als das wol
                        wissentlich <add>sey etc.</add> Also wöllen wir
                            <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> schreyben darümb wol
                            <expan>gelawb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und euch des günnen und im fürbaz durch
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> keins argen darümb gewarten.
                                <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo wir euch lieb oder freuntschaft
                        beweisen möhten, das teten wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Barth<ex>olomei</ex></expan>
<expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
